Scorponok walks over to DarkMouse, He grabs her by the arms and bring 
her face up to his. "You best not mess wih me or I might have to kill 
you." Scorponok throws Darkmouse off to the side. "Hmmm, where should 
I looks for a base?" Scorponok walks down a side of a hill, He looks 
behind him. "Don't just sit there!!!"
